name: v2 Address Expiration Reason
description: FHIR Value set/code system definition for HL7 v2 table 0616 ( Address Expiration Reason)

extension.valueString: The address has been replaced with a corrected version
The address was incorrect and should never have been associated with the individual
The individual associated with the address has moved and is no longer reachable at the address
The associated individual requested that the address be removed from their record
